### [Initial Briefing|155WPM|urgent]

[urgent]We need everyone's attention immediately.[/urgent] //
At 04:12 this morning, our monitoring systems detected unauthorized activity in a production environment. /

## [Impact|145WPM|concerned|0:45-2:15]

### [Scope Block|145WPM|concerned]

The incident was isolated within minutes, /
but customer-facing services experienced intermittent disruption across two regions. //

### [Response Block|150WPM|focused]

[emphasis]No payment data was exposed[/emphasis], /
and the affected infrastructure has already been removed from rotation. //

